Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:06.69,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:11.37,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:29.87,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天這樣的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.52,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:40.49,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏過所有的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.51,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:49.43,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}戀愛笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:53.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手無策 在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投無路 遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:03.20,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己鏡中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:14.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:21.05,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告別 這種答案毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:26.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:22:00.87,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}看看地獄之底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:08.44,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}小心別墮落下去 我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:23.72,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行屍走肉般走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:29.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}頭頂的陽光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.44,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何時你已經淪落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:40.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}連自己名字也都遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.36,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.03,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.94,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:56.65,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如隨之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.64,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:09.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}從寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 聽風帶來山林的迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}請看 指引我們的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:19.91,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}就是斬斷悲哀的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:24.52,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}別害怕 別顫抖 活下去

